Helene Whitney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helene_Whitney 0 Helene Whitney (born Kenyon Fortescue, July 4, 1914 – March 28, 1990) was an American actress who appeared in films in the late 1930s and 1940s. She was known as Helene Reynolds after her marriage.
